#!markdown
# Kitchen Sink Test

Exercises every supported kernel. Use **Run All** to test them in sequence.

## C# — Basic

#!csharp
var greeting = "Hello from C#!";
Console.WriteLine(greeting);
Console.WriteLine($"DateTime: {DateTime.Now}");
Enumerable.Range(1, 5).Select(i => i * i).ToList().ForEach(Console.WriteLine);

#!markdown
## F#

#!fsharp
let squares = [1..5] |> List.map (fun x -> x * x)
printfn "Squares: %A" squares
printfn "Hello from F#! %s" (System.DateTime.Now.ToString())

#!markdown
## PowerShell

#!pwsh
Write-Host "Hello from PowerShell!"
Get-Process | Sort-Object CPU -Descending | Select-Object -First 5 Name, CPU, Id

